# UI Component Selection Guide

**Always use existing primitives. Never recreate.**

## Component Mapping

| Need | Source | Import |
|------|--------|--------|
| Button, Input, Label, Checkbox | shadcn/ui | `@/components/ui/button` |
| Select, Combobox | shadcn/ui | `@/components/ui/select` |
| Dialog, AlertDialog | shadcn/ui (Radix) | `@/components/ui/dialog` |
| Dropdown, Context Menu | shadcn/ui (Radix) | `@/components/ui/dropdown-menu` |
| Popover, Tooltip | shadcn/ui (Radix) | `@/components/ui/popover` |
| Tabs, Accordion | shadcn/ui (Radix) | `@/components/ui/tabs` |
| Drawer, Sheet | Vaul | `@/components/ui/drawer` |
| Toast notifications | Sonner | `import { toast } from 'sonner'` |
| Data Tables | TanStack Table | `@tanstack/react-table` |
| Icons | Lucide React | `import { Icon } from 'lucide-react'` |
| Charts | Recharts | `recharts` |
| Animation | Motion | `import { motion } from 'framer-motion'` |

## Extended Components

KokonutUI registry available for advanced patterns:
- `@/components/kokonutui/*`

## cn() Utility

Always compose Tailwind classes with `cn()`:

```typescript
import { cn } from '@/lib/utils'

<div className={cn('base-classes', conditional && 'conditional-class', className)} />
```

## Before Creating New Components

1. Check `@/components/ui/` for existing primitives
2. Check `@/components/kokonutui/` for extended patterns
3. Check shadcn/ui docs for additional components to install
4. Only create custom if no primitive exists
